items.name: Boss Monster the Dungeon-Building Card Game Wiki
items.title: Boss Monster the Dungeon-Building Card Game Wiki
items.headline: Watch out for the Boss Monster Wikia
items.desc: The Boss Monster Wikia community site was founded by fans of the dungeon building card game Boss Monster. Boss Monster: The Dungeon-Building Card Game is a 2-4 player card game. In the game, players take control of a Boss Monster whose objective is to build a Dungeon that will lure in Heroes and destroy them in order to capture their Souls without taking too many Wounds. The Wikia contains information on the bosses, rooms, spells, heroes, items, cards, rules, and more.

items.title: Building Kasa-Amith Wiki
items.headline: Building Kasa-Amith, an open source fantasy world.
items.desc: Have you ever wanted to create a fantasy world of your own? Tell the story of a great adventurer? Or maybe even discover a new race of people? In Building Kasa-Amith you can. Here you can create, invent, conjure or even tell legends of great heroes thousands of years old. In Building Kasa-Amith you can do almost anything you can think of. Once you are registered you will become a contributor. As a contributor you will help build the world of Kasa-Amith. The goal of this wiki is to create a deep and rich fictional world. Think of it as an encyclopedia and a history book all in one for a fictional world.
